<span class="displaytext">arlington, va -- u.s. senator (candidate full) today issued the following statement on the news concerning senator ted kennedy: <p>"i was very sorry to hear that senator kennedy has taken ill, and like millions of americans, cindy and i anxiously await word of his condition. senator kennedy's role in the u.s. senate cannot be overstated. he is a legendary lawmaker, and i have the highest respect for him. when we have worked together, he has been a skillful, fair and generous partner. i consider it a great privilege to call him my friend. cindy and i are praying for our friend, his wife, vicki and the kennedy family."</p></span>



